#: ../../source/references/4-build-in-strategy-blender.md
msgid "sht"
msgstr "sht"

#: ../../source/references/4-build-in-strategy-blender.md
msgid "`SCRSHT`"
msgstr "`SCRSHT`"

#: ../../source/references/4-build-in-strategy-blender.md
msgid "单均线交叉策略——HT(希尔伯特变换瞬时趋势线)：根据股价与HT线的相对位置设定持仓比例"
